---
title: Italian Beef Burger with Crispy Cheddar, Caramelised Onion & Wedges
description: Sure, everyone rushes to the table when burgers are on the menu, but these ones will get them moving double-quick. That’s because we've topped each tender beef patty with a Cheddar crisp – it adds a special cheesy touch and is super simple to make!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-beef-burger-739ae89e.jpg
